description: Nine people are killed as an oxygen ventilator explodes at a coronavirus ward of a private hospital.
title: Covid-19: Explosion kills nine coronavirus patients in Turkey
title_page: Covid-19: Explosion kills nine coronavirus patients in Turkey - BBC News
maintext: In October, more than 150 patients at a makeshift coronavirus hospital in the Russian region of Chelyabinsk had to be evacuated when an explosion in an "oxygen booth" caused a fire, Russia's emergencies ministry said.
